            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>做美甲，会伤指甲吗？这类人千万不要做美甲！】我隔壁工位的办公室门面担当阿花，最近迷上了做美甲，每次指甲新长出一点，她就立马踏进美甲店。然而还没过2个月，阿花就发毒誓：“再也不做了！”——就在前几天，她像往常那样提起裤子，整块甲板却直接崩断！医生看过她的指甲后，摇摇头说：“你这就是频繁做美甲惹的祸！”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6gf1oe2j20g92k8jvw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6gejhy7j20g921ojw6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6gehappj20g91gjjue.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6gen1t9j20g93itwlh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6gehqh0j20g91fwwha.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hiq6geoo0ug20rr0fe4jq.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
