            <description><![CDATA[【“强迫70岁老爸去文身，邻居都骂我不孝”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[泪]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_lei-4cdf6ee412.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】那天，我刚把我爸硬拉出门，就被堵在自己家门口。门口围满的邻里街坊，像审犯人一样纷纷对我“开炮”——“听说你要带你爸去文身？”“带你爸去文身，考虑过他的感受吗？”“你这样做，别人该怎么看他？”2023年7月，深圳一刺青店发布“免费为阿尔茨海默病患者文身”的贴文，引发网友热议。或许文身，不是最好的办法。但是，除了文身，我还能怎么办呢<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[单身狗]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫新鲜事儿#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4955273375186969" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hiq2f3x1t6j20qo0f0aad.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/VzYubGOCgx089gjv2cgo01041201g0PX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=960x540.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696972319&amp;ssig=ZwPURFX3ZF&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/CeC0A7S3gx089gjuWgMU01041200V2jX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696972319&amp;ssig=gLDlxH%2BpCt&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/H4x3h7Ligx089gjuKDJC01041200AN9P0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696972319&amp;ssig=4Q4JwrXyUB&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4955273375186969" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
